timeline.bodyText:
IMHO you should not assume the status code to be in the [400, 500) range here. Instead, use StatusCodeMapper.from(int, String) which takes care of this ...
For readability I would also explicitly check for OK instead, i.e.
result.isOK() ? Future.succeededFuture() : StatusCodeMapper.from(result.getStatus(), null);

